(53, 1, '2019-12-10 16:07:56', '2019-12-10 09:07:56', '<h2>Ruang<br>Creative<br>Project</h2>		\n		<p>FitFlex\'s Top skilled trainers will get you in shape. Reach the perfect fit with the outfit you\'ve always wanted</p>		\n			<a href=\"#\" role=\"button\">\n						count me in\n					</a>\n			<figure><img width=\"143\" height=\"143\" src=\"http://localhost/webrcp/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/22.png\" alt=\"\" /></figure><h3>Foot work</h3><p>Walking, running, climbing. Your feet will be put to the test.</p>		\n			<figure><img width=\"143\" height=\"143\" src=\"http://localhost/webrcp/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/21.png\" alt=\"\" /></figure><h3>Heart rate</h3><p>The fastest way to reach results is to monitor the progress you make.</p>		\n			<figure><img width=\"143\" height=\"143\" src=\"http://localhost/webrcp/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/20.png\" alt=\"\" /></figure><h3>Weight lifting</h3><p>By slowly raising the weight bar, we are able to built muscles safely.</p>		\n			<h3>Featured Classes</h3>		\n			<h2>Strength & stamina</h2>		\n		<p>In FitFlex\'s Strength and Stamina class, we will delve deep into building the fittest body you can. The class aims to not only shape you up, but also instruct and inform you in the right methods to do weightlifting and working out.</p>		\n			<a href=\"#\" role=\"button\">\n						Sign up\n					</a>\n			<h2>Flexibility postures</h2>		\n		<p>Learn how to maintain a comfortable and healthy posture, with our comprehensive class that goes through the most popular Yoga and Pilates postures. These postures are gears to make your body more flexibile and agile.</p>		\n			<a href=\"#\" role=\"button\">\n						Sign up\n					</a>\n			<h2>achieving your goals</h2>		\n		<p>Getting in shape forces you to face your biggest challenges, and sticking to a regular routine for a long period of time. This class will make sure you know how to focus on the right exercises and workouts to reach your goals. </p>		\n			<a href=\"#\" role=\"button\">\n						Sign up\n					</a>\n			<h3>What Our customers say</h3>		\n										<img width=\"204\" height=\"204\" src=\"http://localhost/webrcp/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/1.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/webrcp/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/1.jpg 204w, http://localhost/webrcp/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/1-150x150.jpg 150w, http://localhost/webrcp/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/1-200x200.jpg 200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 204px) 100vw, 204px\" />											\n				<p>\n					I\'ve managed to stay with  FitFlex 3 times a week, for over 6 months now, and I owe it all to the classes that make you fall in love with the process.\n				</p>\n								<p>Lizzie Thompson</p>\n										<img width=\"204\" height=\"204\" src=\"http://localhost/webrcp/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/2.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/webrcp/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/2.jpg 204w, http://localhost/webrcp/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/2-150x150.jpg 150w, http://localhost/webrcp/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/2-200x200.jpg 200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 204px) 100vw, 204px\" />											\n				<p>\n					I was introduced to FitFlex many years ago, twenty pounds ago in fact. I see a huge benefit with their combination of workout and goal setting.\n				</p>\n								<p>Emma Velasquez</p>\n			<h3>Choose Your PLAN</h3>		\n		<p>Pick a program that best fits your schedule and goals. All plans offer a full money back guarantee.</p>		\n			<h3>Starter</h3>		\n			<h2>$29</h2>		\n		<p>/month</p>		\n			<p>Open Gym</p>		\n			<p>Gymnastics</p>		\n			<p>CrossFit</p>		\n			<p>Yoga</p>		\n			<p>Personal Trainer</p>		\n			<a href=\"#\" role=\"button\">\n						Start Today\n					</a>\n			<h3>Basic</h3>		\n			<h2>$49</h2>		\n		<p>/month</p>		\n			<p>Open Gym</p>		\n			<p>Gymnastics</p>		\n			<p>CrossFit</p>		\n			<p>Yoga</p>		\n			<p>Personal Trainer</p>		\n			<a href=\"#\" role=\"button\">\n						Start Today\n					</a>\n			<h3>Pro</h3>		\n			<h2>$99</h2>		\n		<p>/month</p>		\n			<p>Open Gym</p>		\n			<p>Gymnastics</p>		\n			<p>CrossFit</p>		\n			<p>Yoga</p>		\n			<p>Personal Trainer</p>		\n			<a href=\"#\" role=\"button\">\n						Start Today\n					</a>', 'Profile', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'profile', '', '', '2019-12-10 19:06:48', '2019-12-10 12:06:48', '', 0, 'http://localhost/webrcp/?page_id=53', 0, 'page', '', 0),
